(105, 31, 'hazard', 'a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:"title";s:37:"Reaching for objects and bending down";s:14:"hazard_content";s:360:"Add additional shelves and hooks under cabinets, or install a wall rack.\r\nInstall drawer organizers and pull-out shelving. Use lever or U-shaped pulls or handles or touch latches (in current house).\r\nHave a sturdy stepladder with safety bar/handgrip available.\r\nPlace heavier and frequently used items within easy reach.\r\nElevated/wall oven (in current house).";}i:1;a:2:{s:5:"title";s:19:"Inadequate lighting";s:14:"hazard_content";s:246:"Install good ceiling lighting and task lighting where food is prepared.\r\nLighting should be non-glare, non-reflective, using and low-sheen laminates.\r\nInstall a faucet with a single lever-handle that is easy to turn on and off (in current house).";}i:2;a:2:{s:5:"title";s:31:"Inadequate support when cooking";s:14:"hazard_content";s:124:"Stool for sitting while completing tasks (in current house).\r\nVariable height countertops.\r\nRound corners on all countertops";}}'),
